✅ Day 3 – Story & Insights

---

Story (Me)

Every success has a long journey.
Every journey toward progress needs much effort, and every effort comes with many failures.
Every person should know that the path to success is full of challenges, but they can pass this path just by using strong support, having confidence, and putting in much effort.


---

Words: Journey • Confident • Effort • Support • Progress

---

What I Learned

✔️ Modal verbs → base form of verb (no “to” after modals)

✔️ Confident “by” → use verb+i

✔️ Confidentdent (adj.) → need “confidence” (noun)

✔️ common phrases: put in effort is natural English
